# Environment Variables for Turborepo AI Chat Demo

# This monorepo uses environment variables in specific packages
# See apps/web/.env.example for the web application's environment variables

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy apps/web/.env.local.example to apps/web/.env.local
# 2. Fill in your API keys in apps/web/.env.local
# 3. Do not commit .env.local files to version control

# Required for the chat application:
# - OPENAI_API_KEY: Your OpenAI API key for GPT-4
# - HUGGINGFACE_ENDPOINT_URL: Your HuggingFace TGI endpoint URL for SmolLM
# - HUGGINGFACE_API_KEY: Your HuggingFace API token